songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
They've been around me
They've been killing me
They've been feeling me
They've loved me
What a disaster
They've been around me

[Verse 1]
People were surrounding me, every time
All of you are wasting my time
But you don't cost a dime
This shit ain't hilarious
Your so fucking delirious
This isn't delicious

[Pre-Chorus]
I don't know how the years will go down, it's alright
Let's make the most of every moment, tonight

[Chorus]
They've been around me
They've been killing me
They've been feeling me
They've loved me
What a disaster
They've been around me

[Verse 2]
Doesn't know any shit about it
This wouldn't be okay if you weren't here
We're phenomenal, that's lit
Two minutes in and where you at?
Where?

[Pre-Chorus]
I don't know how the years will go down, it's alright
Let's make the most of every moment, tonight

[Chorus]
They've been around me
They've been killing me
They've been feeling me
They've loved me
What a disaster
They've been around me

[Bridge]
I've been through everything
I've been through everything
Same stress, same shit

[Chorus]
They've been around me
They've been killing me
They've been feeling me
They've loved me
What a disaster
They've been around me
songs.title: Around Me
